quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  7,54,Your Lord est 1 DI kre heavens ter 6 tag tiam assumed all auxtoritat. Nokt overtakes tag gxi pursues gxi persistently sun lun stel committed dejxor His ordon! Absolutely Li controls all creation all ordon. Exalted est DI Lord univers
  7,55,Vi worship your Lord publicly privately; Li ne am transgressors
  7,56,Ne corrupt ter gxi set rekt worship Him reverence esper! Surely di mercy est attainable per des righteous
  7,57,Li est 1 who send vent bon omen mercy el His man! Once ili gather heavy nub ni sxofor them dead land send down akv therefrom produkt gxi all kinds da frukt! Ni tiel resurrect dead ke vi pren heed
  7,58,Bon land readily produkt its plant las its Lord while mav land barely produkt anything util. Ni tiel eksplik revelations popol est appreciative